title: Public Enemy Number 1 (Part 2)
description:
Public Enemy Number 1 (Part 2)     FINAL

Jacques Mesrine is back in France after his brazen assault on the maximum-security prison from which he daringly escaped. Once again in police custody and facing stern justice for his crimes, the "man of a thousand faces" escapes directly from the courtroom after kidnapping the judge at gunpoint. As Mesrine continues to author his own legend through the media and his own memoirs, he becomes a household name and anti-hero across all of France. The life of Jacques Mesrine comes once and for all to a full bloody circle in a climax only fitting for France's Public Enemy #1.
